--- Dependencies ---

Ignore node_modules folders in the root, /client, /server, etc.

**/node_modules

--- Environment Variables (CRITICAL) ---

Ignore all .env files EXCEPT .env.example (which is safe to commit)

This catches .env, .env.local, .env.development, .env.production, etc.

These files contain your secret API keys and database URI!

.env
.env.*
!.env.example

